body_html:
@fifothekid Is this build with or without MKL & MKLDNN?

For the concern, you may better install absl-py as well as protobuf before the build.
Please try to build tf_python_api and then estimator_python_api, if anything failed, could you paste the failure information?
(With cmake options unchanged)

As I expect, it may fail for estimator_python_api but will success for tf_python_api

body:
@fifothekid Is this build with or without MKL & MKLDNN?

For the concern, you may better install `absl-py` as well as `protobuf` before the build.
Please try to build `tf_python_api` and then `estimator_python_api`, if anything failed, could you paste the failure information?
(With cmake options unchanged)

As I expect, it may fail for `estimator_python_api` but will success for `tf_python_api`
